5608  s->malloc_size = rt->malloc_state.malloc_size;
5609  s->malloc_limit = rt->malloc_state.malloc_limit;
5610 
5611  s->memory_used_count = 2; /* rt + rt->class_array */
5612  s->memory_used_size = sizeof(JSRuntime) + sizeof(JSValue) * rt->class_count;
5613 
5614  list_for_each(el, &rt->context_list) {
5615  JSContext *ctx = list_entry(el, JSContext, link);
5616  JSShape *sh = ctx->array_shape;
5617  s->memory_used_count += 2; /* ctx + ctx->class_proto */
5618  s->memory_used_size += sizeof(JSContext) +
5619  sizeof(JSValue) * rt->class_count;
5620  s->binary_object_count += ctx->binary_object_count;
5621  s->binary_object_size += ctx->binary_object_size;
5622 
5623  /* the hashed shapes are counted separately */
5624  if (sh && !sh->is_hashed) {
5625  int hash_size = sh->prop_hash_mask + 1;
5626  s->shape_count++;
5627  s->shape_size += get_shape_size(hash_size, sh->prop_size);
5628  }
5629  list_for_each(el1, &ctx->loaded_modules) {
5630  JSModuleDef *m = list_entry(el1, JSModuleDef, link);
5631  s->memory_used_count += 1;
5632  s->memory_used_size += sizeof(*m);
5633  if (m->req_module_entries) {
5634  s->memory_used_count += 1;
5635  s->memory_used_size += m->req_module_entries_count * sizeof(*m->req_module_entries);
5636  }
5637  if (m->export_entries) {
5638  s->memory_used_count += 1;
5639  s->memory_used_size += m->export_entries_count * sizeof(*m->export_entries);
5640  for (i = 0; i < m->export_entries_count; i++) {
5641  JSExportEntry *me = &m->export_entries[i];
5642  if (me->export_type == JS_EXPORT_TYPE_LOCAL && me->u.local.var_ref) {
5643  /* potential multiple count */
5644  s->memory_used_count += 1;
5645  compute_value_size(me->u.local.var_ref->value, hp);
5646  }
5647  }
5648  }
5649  if (m->star_export_entries) {
5650  s->memory_used_count += 1;
5651  s->memory_used_size += m->star_export_entries_count * sizeof(*m->star_export_entries);
5652  }
5653  if (m->import_entries) {
5654  s->memory_used_count += 1;
5655  s->memory_used_size += m->import_entries_count * sizeof(*m->import_entries);
5656  }
5657  compute_value_size(m->module_ns, hp);
5658  compute_value_size(m->func_obj, hp);
5659  }
5660  }
5661 
5662  list_for_each(el, &rt->gc_obj_list) {
5663  JSGCObjectHeader *gp = list_entry(el, JSGCObjectHeader, link);
5664  JSObject *p;
5665  JSShape *sh;
5666  JSShapeProperty *prs;
5667 
5668  /* XXX: could count the other GC object types too */
5669  if (gp->gc_obj_type == JS_GC_OBJ_TYPE_FUNCTION_BYTECODE) {
5670  compute_bytecode_size((JSFunctionBytecode *)gp, hp);
5671  continue;
5672  } else if (gp->gc_obj_type != JS_GC_OBJ_TYPE_JS_OBJECT) {
5673  continue;
5674  }
5675  p = (JSObject *)gp;
5676  sh = p->shape;
5677  s->obj_count++;
5678  if (p->prop) {
5679  s->memory_used_count++;
5680  s->prop_size += sh->prop_size * sizeof(*p->prop);
5681  s->prop_count += sh->prop_count;
5682  prs = get_shape_prop(sh);
5683  for(i = 0; i < sh->prop_count; i++) {
5684  JSProperty *pr = &p->prop[i];
5685  if (prs->atom != JS_ATOM_NULL && !(prs->flags & JS_PROP_TMASK)) {
5686  compute_value_size(pr->u.value, hp);
5687  }
5688  prs++;
5689  }
5690  }
5691  /* the hashed shapes are counted separately */
5692  if (!sh->is_hashed) {
5693  int hash_size = sh->prop_hash_mask + 1;
5694  s->shape_count++;
5695  s->shape_size += get_shape_size(hash_size, sh->prop_size);
5696  }
5697 
5698  switch(p->class_id) {
5699  case JS_CLASS_ARRAY: /* u.array | length */
5700  case JS_CLASS_ARGUMENTS: /* u.array | length */
5701  s->array_count++;
5702  if (p->fast_array) {
5703  s->fast_array_count++;
5704  if (p->u.array.u.values) {
5705  s->memory_used_count++;
5706  s->memory_used_size += p->u.array.count *
5707  sizeof(*p->u.array.u.values);
5708  s->fast_array_elements += p->u.array.count;
5709  for (i = 0; i < p->u.array.count; i++) {
5710  compute_value_size(p->u.array.u.values[i], hp);
5711  }
5712  }
5713  }
5714  break;
5715  case JS_CLASS_NUMBER: /* u.object_data */
5716  case JS_CLASS_STRING: /* u.object_data */
5717  case JS_CLASS_BOOLEAN: /* u.object_data */
5718  case JS_CLASS_SYMBOL: /* u.object_data */
5719  case JS_CLASS_DATE: /* u.object_data */
5720 #ifdef CONFIG_BIGNUM
5721  case JS_CLASS_BIG_INT: /* u.object_data */
5722  case JS_CLASS_BIG_FLOAT: /* u.object_data */
5723 #endif
5724  compute_value_size(p->u.object_data, hp);
5725  break;
5726  case JS_CLASS_C_FUNCTION: /* u.cfunc */
5727  s->c_func_count++;
5728  break;
5729  case JS_CLASS_BYTECODE_FUNCTION: /* u.func */
5730  {
5731  JSFunctionBytecode *b = p->u.func.function_bytecode;
5732  JSVarRef **var_refs = p->u.func.var_refs;
5733  /* home_object: object will be accounted for in list scan */
5734  if (var_refs) {
5735  s->memory_used_count++;
5736  s->js_func_size += b->closure_var_count * sizeof(*var_refs);
5737  for (i = 0; i < b->closure_var_count; i++) {
5738  if (var_refs[i]) {
5739  double ref_count = var_refs[i]->header.ref_count;
5740  s->memory_used_count += 1 / ref_count;
5741  s->js_func_size += sizeof(*var_refs[i]) / ref_count;
5742  /* handle non object closed values */
5743  if (var_refs[i]->pvalue == &var_refs[i]->value) {
5744  /* potential multiple count */
5745  compute_value_size(var_refs[i]->value, hp);
5746  }
5747  }
5748  }
5749  }
5750  }
5751  break;
5752  case JS_CLASS_BOUND_FUNCTION: /* u.bound_function */
5753  {
5754  JSBoundFunction *bf = p->u.bound_function;
5755  /* func_obj and this_val are objects */
5756  for (i = 0; i < bf->argc; i++) {
5757  compute_value_size(bf->argv[i], hp);
5758  }
5759  s->memory_used_count += 1;
5760  s->memory_used_size += sizeof(*bf) + bf->argc * sizeof(*bf->argv);
5761  }
5762  break;
5763  case JS_CLASS_C_FUNCTION_DATA: /* u.c_function_data_record */
5764  {
5765  JSCFunctionDataRecord *fd = p->u.c_function_data_record;
5766  if (fd) {
5767  for (i = 0; i < fd->data_len; i++) {
5768  compute_value_size(fd->data[i], hp);
5769  }
5770  s->memory_used_count += 1;
5771  s->memory_used_size += sizeof(*fd) + fd->data_len * sizeof(*fd->data);
5772  }
5773  }
5774  break;
5775  case JS_CLASS_REGEXP: /* u.regexp */
5776  compute_jsstring_size(p->u.regexp.pattern, hp);
5777  compute_jsstring_size(p->u.regexp.bytecode, hp);
5778  break;
5779 
5780  case JS_CLASS_FOR_IN_ITERATOR: /* u.for_in_iterator */
5781  {
5782  JSForInIterator *it = p->u.for_in_iterator;
5783  if (it) {
5784  compute_value_size(it->obj, hp);
5785  s->memory_used_count += 1;
5786  s->memory_used_size += sizeof(*it);
5787  }
5788  }
5789  break;
5790  case JS_CLASS_ARRAY_BUFFER: /* u.array_buffer */
5791  case JS_CLASS_SHARED_ARRAY_BUFFER: /* u.array_buffer */
5792  {
5793  JSArrayBuffer *abuf = p->u.array_buffer;
5794  if (abuf) {
5795  s->memory_used_count += 1;
5796  s->memory_used_size += sizeof(*abuf);
5797  if (abuf->data) {
5798  s->memory_used_count += 1;
5799  s->memory_used_size += abuf->byte_length;
5800  }
5801  }
5802  }
5803  break;
5804  case JS_CLASS_GENERATOR: /* u.generator_data */
5805  case JS_CLASS_UINT8C_ARRAY: /* u.typed_array / u.array */
5806  case JS_CLASS_INT8_ARRAY: /* u.typed_array / u.array */
5807  case JS_CLASS_UINT8_ARRAY: /* u.typed_array / u.array */
5808  case JS_CLASS_INT16_ARRAY: /* u.typed_array / u.array */
5809  case JS_CLASS_UINT16_ARRAY: /* u.typed_array / u.array */
5810  case JS_CLASS_INT32_ARRAY: /* u.typed_array / u.array */
5811  case JS_CLASS_UINT32_ARRAY: /* u.typed_array / u.array */
5812 #ifdef CONFIG_BIGNUM
5813  case JS_CLASS_BIG_INT64_ARRAY: /* u.typed_array / u.array */
5814  case JS_CLASS_BIG_UINT64_ARRAY: /* u.typed_array / u.array */
5815 #endif
5816  case JS_CLASS_FLOAT32_ARRAY: /* u.typed_array / u.array */
5817  case JS_CLASS_FLOAT64_ARRAY: /* u.typed_array / u.array */
5818  case JS_CLASS_DATAVIEW: /* u.typed_array */
5819 #ifdef CONFIG_BIGNUM
5820  case JS_CLASS_FLOAT_ENV: /* u.float_env */
5821 #endif
5822  case JS_CLASS_MAP: /* u.map_state */
5823  case JS_CLASS_SET: /* u.map_state */
5824  case JS_CLASS_WEAKMAP: /* u.map_state */
5825  case JS_CLASS_WEAKSET: /* u.map_state */
5826  case JS_CLASS_MAP_ITERATOR: /* u.map_iterator_data */
5827  case JS_CLASS_SET_ITERATOR: /* u.map_iterator_data */
5828  case JS_CLASS_ARRAY_ITERATOR: /* u.array_iterator_data */
5829  case JS_CLASS_STRING_ITERATOR: /* u.array_iterator_data */
5830  case JS_CLASS_PROXY: /* u.proxy_data */
5831  case JS_CLASS_PROMISE: /* u.promise_data */
5832  case JS_CLASS_PROMISE_RESOLVE_FUNCTION: /* u.promise_function_data */
5833  case JS_CLASS_PROMISE_REJECT_FUNCTION: /* u.promise_function_data */
5834  case JS_CLASS_ASYNC_FUNCTION_RESOLVE: /* u.async_function_data */
5835  case JS_CLASS_ASYNC_FUNCTION_REJECT: /* u.async_function_data */
5836  case JS_CLASS_ASYNC_FROM_SYNC_ITERATOR: /* u.async_from_sync_iterator_data */
5837  case JS_CLASS_ASYNC_GENERATOR: /* u.async_generator_data */
5838  /* TODO */
5839  default:
5840  /* XXX: class definition should have an opaque block size */
5841  if (p->u.opaque) {
5842  s->memory_used_count += 1;
5843  }
5844  break;
5845  }
5846  }
5847  s->obj_size += s->obj_count * sizeof(JSObject);
5848 
5849  /* hashed shapes */
5850  s->memory_used_count++; /* rt->shape_hash */
5851  s->memory_used_size += sizeof(rt->shape_hash[0]) * rt->shape_hash_size;
5852  for(i = 0; i < rt->shape_hash_size; i++) {
5853  JSShape *sh;
5854  for(sh = rt->shape_hash[i]; sh != NULL; sh = sh->shape_hash_next) {
5855  int hash_size = sh->prop_hash_mask + 1;
5856  s->shape_count++;
5857  s->shape_size += get_shape_size(hash_size, sh->prop_size);
5858  }
5859  }
5860 
5861  /* atoms */
5862  s->memory_used_count += 2; /* rt->atom_array, rt->atom_hash */
5863  s->atom_count = rt->atom_count;
5864  s->atom_size = sizeof(rt->atom_array[0]) * rt->atom_size +
5865  sizeof(rt->atom_hash[0]) * rt->atom_hash_size;
5866  for(i = 0; i < rt->atom_size; i++) {
5867  JSAtomStruct *p = rt->atom_array[i];
5868  if (!atom_is_free(p)) {
5869  s->atom_size += (sizeof(*p) + (p->len << p->is_wide_char) +
5870  1 - p->is_wide_char);
5871  }
5872  }
5873  s->str_count = round(mem.str_count);
5874  s->str_size = round(mem.str_size);
5875  s->js_func_count = mem.js_func_count;
5876  s->js_func_size = round(mem.js_func_size);
5877  s->js_func_code_size = mem.js_func_code_size;
5878  s->js_func_pc2line_count = mem.js_func_pc2line_count;
5879  s->js_func_pc2line_size = mem.js_func_pc2line_size;
5880  s->memory_used_count += round(mem.memory_used_count) +
5881  s->atom_count + s->str_count +
5882  s->obj_count + s->shape_count +
5883  s->js_func_count + s->js_func_pc2line_count;
5884  s->memory_used_size += s->atom_size + s->str_size +
5885  s->obj_size + s->prop_size + s->shape_size +
5886  s->js_func_size + s->js_func_code_size + s->js_func_pc2line_size;
5887 }

8763  set_value(ctx, &p->u.array.u.values[idx], JS_DupValue(ctx, val));
8764  }
8765  return TRUE;
8766  }
8767  }
8768  } else if (p->class_id >= JS_CLASS_UINT8C_ARRAY &&
8769  p->class_id <= JS_CLASS_FLOAT64_ARRAY) {
8770  JSValue num;
8771  int ret;
8772 
8773  if (!__JS_AtomIsTaggedInt(prop)) {
8774  /* slow path with to handle all numeric indexes */
8775  num = JS_AtomIsNumericIndex1(ctx, prop);
8776  if (JS_IsUndefined(num))
8777  goto typed_array_done;
8778  if (JS_IsException(num))
8779  return -1;
8780  ret = JS_NumberIsInteger(ctx, num);
8781  if (ret < 0) {
8782  JS_FreeValue(ctx, num);
8783  return -1;
8784  }
8785  if (!ret) {
8786  JS_FreeValue(ctx, num);
8787  return JS_ThrowTypeErrorOrFalse(ctx, flags, "non integer index in typed array");
8788  }
8789  ret = JS_NumberIsNegativeOrMinusZero(ctx, num);
8790  JS_FreeValue(ctx, num);
8791  if (ret) {
8792  return JS_ThrowTypeErrorOrFalse(ctx, flags, "negative index in typed array");
8793  }
8794  if (!__JS_AtomIsTaggedInt(prop))
8795  goto typed_array_oob;
8796  }
8797  idx = __JS_AtomToUInt32(prop);
8798  /* if the typed array is detached, p->u.array.count = 0 */
8799  if (idx >= typed_array_get_length(ctx, p)) {
8800  typed_array_oob:
8801  return JS_ThrowTypeErrorOrFalse(ctx, flags, "out-of-bound index in typed array");
8802  }
8803  prop_flags = get_prop_flags(flags, JS_PROP_ENUMERABLE | JS_PROP_WRITABLE);
8804  if (flags & (JS_PROP_HAS_GET | JS_PROP_HAS_SET) ||
8805  prop_flags != (JS_PROP_ENUMERABLE | JS_PROP_WRITABLE)) {
8806  return JS_ThrowTypeErrorOrFalse(ctx, flags, "invalid descriptor flags");
8807  }
8808  if (flags & JS_PROP_HAS_VALUE) {
8809  return JS_SetPropertyValue(ctx, this_obj, JS_NewInt32(ctx, idx), JS_DupValue(ctx, val), flags);
8810  }
8811  return TRUE;
8812  typed_array_done: ;
8813  }
8814  }
8815 
8816  return JS_CreateProperty(ctx, p, prop, val, getter, setter, flags);
8817 }

42508  JSObject *p = JS_VALUE_GET_OBJ(space);
42509  if (p->class_id == JS_CLASS_NUMBER) {
42510  space = JS_ToNumberFree(ctx, space);
42511  } else if (p->class_id == JS_CLASS_STRING) {
42512  space = JS_ToStringFree(ctx, space);
42513  }
42514  if (JS_IsException(space)) {
42515  JS_FreeValue(ctx, space);
42516  goto exception;
42517  }
42518  }
42519  if (JS_IsNumber(space)) {
42520  int n;
42521  if (JS_ToInt32Clamp(ctx, &n, space, 0, 10, 0))
42522  goto exception;
42523  jsc->gap = JS_NewStringLen(ctx, " ", n);
42524  } else if (JS_IsString(space)) {
42525  JSString *p = JS_VALUE_GET_STRING(space);
42526  jsc->gap = js_sub_string(ctx, p, 0, min_int(p->len, 10));
42527  } else {
42528  jsc->gap = JS_DupValue(ctx, jsc->empty);
42529  }
42530  JS_FreeValue(ctx, space);
42531  if (JS_IsException(jsc->gap))
42532  goto exception;
42533  wrapper = JS_NewObject(ctx);
42534  if (JS_IsException(wrapper))
42535  goto exception;
42536  if (JS_DefinePropertyValue(ctx, wrapper, JS_ATOM_empty_string,
42537  JS_DupValue(ctx, obj), JS_PROP_C_W_E) < 0)
42538  goto exception;
42539  val = JS_DupValue(ctx, obj);
42540 
42541  val = js_json_check(ctx, jsc, wrapper, val, jsc->empty);
42542  if (JS_IsException(val))
42543  goto exception;
42544  if (JS_IsUndefined(val)) {
42545  ret = JS_UNDEFINED;
42546  goto done1;
42547  }
42548  if (js_json_to_str(ctx, jsc, wrapper, val, jsc->empty))
42549  goto exception;
42550 
42551  ret = string_buffer_end(jsc->b);
42552  goto done;
42553 
42554 exception:
42555  ret = JS_EXCEPTION;
42556 done1:
42557  string_buffer_free(jsc->b);
42558 done:
42559  JS_FreeValue(ctx, wrapper);
42560  JS_FreeValue(ctx, jsc->empty);
42561  JS_FreeValue(ctx, jsc->gap);
42562  JS_FreeValue(ctx, jsc->property_list);
42563  JS_FreeValue(ctx, jsc->stack);
42564  return ret;
42565 }
